      <title>希腊总理根据欧洲公投结果改组内阁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/greek-premier-reshuffles-his-cabinet-after-european-vote-outcome</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于周日的欧洲议会选举结果不及预期，希腊总理基里亚科斯·米佐塔基斯于周五改组内阁。]]></description>
